<title key="Bustard neck, stuffed, and roasted">Von dem <ingredient commodity="Q107246439" en="bustard neck">trappem hallse</ingredient></title> ALso 
<instruction>vuell des <alternative reason="ingredient"><ingredient commodity="Q107246439" en="bustard neck">trappem hals</ingredient> oder ander <ingredient en="poultry" commodity="Q178559">vogel</ingredient></alternative></instruction> 
<instruction>nym <ingredient en="pork" commodity="Q191768">sweinen vleisch</ingredient> herte <ingredient en="chicken egg" commodity="Q15260613">ayr</ingredient> <ingredient en="common sage" commodity="Q1111359">salua</ingredient> vnd <ingredient en="herb" commodity="Q207123">kraut</ingredient></instruction> 
<instruction>hakch das alles zusamen</instruction> vnd 
<instruction>full in domit den <ingredient commodity="Q107246439" en="bustard neck">hals</ingredient></instruction> vnd 
<instruction>seud in so er gar sey gesoten</instruction> so 
<instruction>leg in also haissen auf den <tool en="grate" commodity="Q96279691">rost</tool></instruction> 
<instruction>beslach in <alternative reason="ingredient">mit <ingredient en="chicken egg" commodity="Q15260613">ayren</ingredient> oder mit <ingredient commodity="Q107262035" en="egg dough">ayrtaig</ingredient></alternative></instruction> 
<instruction>betreuff in mit <ingredient en="lard" commodity="Q72827">smalcz</ingredient></instruction> vnd 
<instruction>nym <ingredient en="saffron" commodity="Q25434">saffran</ingredient> vnd <ingredient en="parsley" commodity="Q25284">petersil</ingredient> vnd <ingredient en="fennel" commodity="Q27658833">phenich</ingredient></instruction> 
<instruction>mal das auf ain <dish en="sauce" commodity="Q178359">condiment</dish> so du pest machst</instruction> vnd <closer>gib es hin</closer></div></body></text></TEI>